<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to <%= @company_name %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 0;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #3b82f6;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 0;
    }
    .highlight {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 20px;
      border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #3b82f6;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1><%= @company_name %></h1>
    <p>Building Digital Excellence</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>Hi <%= @lead.first_name %>,</h2>

    <p>Thank you for reaching out about your <strong><%= @lead.project_type_display %></strong> project. We're excited to learn more about your vision and how we can help bring it to life.</p>

    <div class="highlight">
      <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Review</strong>: Our team is carefully reviewing your project requirements</li>
        <li><strong>Analysis</strong>: We'll analyze the technical approach and create initial recommendations</li>
        <li><strong>Connection</strong>: A senior team member will reach out within <strong><%= @lead.response_time_target %></strong></li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <h3>Your Project Overview:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Project Type:</strong> <%= @lead.project_type_display %></li>
      <li><strong>Timeline:</strong> <%= @lead.timeline_display %></li>
      <li><strong>Budget Range:</strong> <%= @lead.budget_range_display %></li>
    </ul>

    <p>In the meantime, here are some resources that might interest you:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="<%= root_url %>">View Our Portfolio</a> - See similar projects we've completed</li>
      <li><a href="<%= projects_url %>">Case Studies</a> - Detailed project breakdowns</li>
      <li><a href="<%= about_url %>">About Us</a> - Learn about our team and approach</li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you have any urgent questions or additional information to share, feel free to reply to this email. Our team monitors responses closely.</p>

    <p>Looking forward to discussing your project!</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>
    <strong>The <%= @company_name %> Team</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>
      <%= @company_name %><br>
      <%= link_to 'Visit Our Website', root_url %> |
      <%= link_to 'View Portfolio', projects_url %>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
      You're receiving this email because you contacted us about a project.
      If you didn't submit this inquiry, please <%= link_to 'let us know', contact_url %>.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>